text: Ethan Christopher Dobbelaere (born November 14, 2002) is an American soccer player who plays as a midfielder for Seattle Sounders FC in Major League Soccer. ==Career== On June 15, 2020 Dobbelaere signed a Homegrown Players contract with the Seattle Sounders coming out of the Sounders Academy. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Association football midfielders Category:American soccer players Category:Seattle Sounders FC players Category:Tacoma Defiance players Category:USL Championship players Category:Soccer players from Washington (state) Category:Sportspeople from Seattle Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Homegrown Players (MLS)
